snippet.title: Botany Manor - Official Demo Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description:
Take a tour of the world of Botany Manor, see gameplay, view recipes, and more in this latest trailer for the upcoming exploration puzzle game. A demo for Botany Manor is available now on Steam. Set in a stately home in 19th century England, you play as inhabitant Arabella Greene, a retired botanist. Explore your house and gardens, filled with research, to figure out the ideal habitat of forgotten flora. Grow each plant to discover the mysterious qualities they hold. Botany Manor is coming to PC, Xbox, and Nintendo Switch.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
